Q1
ANS:

Number	Permission Type	Symbol
0	No Permission	---
1	Execute	--x
2	Write	-w-
3	Execute + Write	-wx
4	Read	r--
5	Read + Execute	r-x
6	Read +Write	rw-
7	Read + Write +Execute	rwx


    USER GROUP ALL
eg:  -rw-rw-r-- 1 aman aman 0 Sep  8 20:15 a.txt
